# Feature flag use cases
direction: down

Title: "FEATURE FLAGS HAVE FOUR DISTINCT USE CASES\n(Pete Hodgson, martinfowler.com)\nEach has different lifetime, owner, audience" {
  style: { fill: "#fff4c2"; stroke: "#bf360c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 10 }
}

Release: "RELEASE TOGGLES" {
  style: { fill: "#bbdefb"; stroke: "#0d47a1"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
  Detail: "Ship in-progress features dark\nEnable when ready\nLIFETIME: days\u2013weeks\nOWNER: dev team\nAUDIENCE: gradual user rollout\nREMOVE: as soon as 100% rolled out"
}

Experiment: "EXPERIMENT TOGGLES" {
  style: { fill: "#c8e6c9"; stroke: "#1b5e20"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
  Detail: "A/B test: 50% see variant A, 50% B\nMeasure conversion / retention / etc\nLIFETIME: weeks\u2013months (until significance)\nOWNER: product / data team\nAUDIENCE: randomized cohorts\nREMOVE: after winner picked"
}

Ops: "OPS TOGGLES (KILL SWITCHES)" {
  style: { fill: "#ffe0b2"; stroke: "#bf360c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
  Detail: "Disable a feature during incident\nThrottle expensive feature under load\nTurn off non-critical flows\nLIFETIME: long-lived (always there)\nOWNER: ops / SRE\nAUDIENCE: all users (binary)\nREMOVE: never; live operational tool"
}

Permission: "PERMISSION / ENTITLEMENT TOGGLES" {
  style: { fill: "#e1bee7"; stroke: "#4a148c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
  Detail: "Enterprise plan sees feature X\nFree plan does not\nFriends-of-employees beta\nLIFETIME: permanent\nOWNER: product\nAUDIENCE: per-user / per-segment\nREMOVE: never; a business rule"
}

Warning: "ANTI-PATTERN: 'flag debt'\nFlags left lying around for years.\nBoth code paths still maintained.\nEvery flag is permanent technical debt.\n\nFIX: track lifetime per flag; have a removal date; audit quarterly." {
  shape: rectangle
  style: { fill: "#ffcdd2"; stroke: "#b71c1c"; stroke-width: 2; border-radius: 8 }
}

Title -> Release; Title -> Experiment; Title -> Ops; Title -> Permission
Release -> Warning; Experiment -> Warning
